        Organic Minimalism
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-[#64748b] text-[15px] md:text-[16px] leading-[1.8] font-light mb-6"
      >
        Minimalism is often mistaken for coldness. At de Aurimori, we practice
        "Organic Minimalism"—a reduction that honors the warmth of natural
        materials and the imperfect beauty of the artisan's hand.
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-[#64748b] text-[15px] md:text-[16px] leading-[1.8] font-light"
      >
        It is the synthesis of modern precision and natural unpredictability. A
        sharp line against a rough stone; a perfectly white wall reflecting the
        amber of a setting sun.
      </p>
